TITLE: Configuring Inputs and Named Inputs for Task Caching
DESCRIPTION: Example showing how to define namedInputs for reuse across multiple targets and how to reference them in a target's inputs configuration along with external dependencies.
SOURCE: https://github.com/nrwl/nx/blob/master/docs/shared/reference/project-configuration.md#2025-04-22_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: jsonc
CODE:
