TITLE: Updating Scripts in package.json with Nx Commands (Diff JSON)
DESCRIPTION: This diff snippet shows the updates Nx makes to the package.json scripts section, replacing existing commands with Nx commands that have caching enabled. It demonstrates the integration of plugins such as @nx/next/plugin and @nx/eslint/plugin.
