SOURCE: https://github.com/nrwl/nx/blob/master/nx-dev/tutorial/src/content/tutorial/1-ts-packages/2-smart-monorepo/6-sync-ts-references/content.mdx#_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
export function getRandomItem<T>(arr: T[]): T {
  return arr[Math.floor(Math.random() * arr.length)];
}
```

