TITLE: Implementing Custom Hasher - Mimic Nx Hasher
DESCRIPTION: This TypeScript code implements a custom hasher that mimics the default hashing algorithm used by Nx, returning the result of `context.hasher.hashTask(task)`. This provides a basic example of a custom hasher that effectively replicates Nx's default behavior.
SOURCE: https://github.com/nrwl/nx/blob/master/docs/shared/recipes/plugins/local-executors.md#_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
import { CustomHasher, Task, HasherContext } from '@nx/devkit';

export const mimicNxHasher: CustomHasher = async (
  task: Task,
  context: HasherContext
) => {
  return context.hasher.hashTask(task);
};

export default mimicNxHasher;
```

