TITLE: Configuring CircleCI Workflow with Nx Orb
DESCRIPTION: A CircleCI configuration file that sets up a CI workflow using the Nx Orb, enabling distributed builds, format checking, and running affected commands for lint, test, build, and end-to-end testing
