TITLE: Manual DTE Assignment Rules Configuration in YAML
DESCRIPTION: This YAML code sets up assignment rules for manual distributed task execution (DTE) using different agent types with specified parallelism values. It emphasizes the importance of matching agent types with the 'run-on' property in task distribution.
