TITLE: Configuring Build and Publish Targets in project.json
DESCRIPTION: Updates the project.json file to include both the build target and a new publish target. The publish target depends on the build target and uses the nx-cloud CLI to publish the rules.
SOURCE: https://github.com/nrwl/nx/blob/master/docs/nx-cloud/enterprise/conformance/publish-conformance-rules-to-nx-cloud.md#2025-04-22_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: jsonc
CODE:
```
{
  // ...any existing project.json content
  "targets": {
    "build": {
      "executor": "@nx/conformance:bundle-rules",
      "outputs": ["{options.outputPath}"],
      "options": {
        "outputPath": "{projectRoot}/dist"
      }
    },
    "publish": {
      "dependsOn": ["build"],
      "command": "npx nx-cloud publish-conformance-rules {projectRoot}/dist"
    }
  }
}
```

