TITLE: Configuring Complex CI Pipeline with Artifact Sharing in YAML
DESCRIPTION: This YAML snippet demonstrates a traditional CI pipeline configuration with multiple jobs, dependencies, and artifact sharing. It illustrates the complexity of managing task dependencies and file sharing between jobs in a low-level, explicit manner.
SOURCE: https://github.com/nrwl/nx/blob/master/docs/blog/2024-02-07-fast-effortless-ci.md#2025-04-22_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: yaml
