TITLE: Defining ExecutorsJson Interface in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet defines the ExecutorsJson interface with two optional properties: 'builders' and 'executors'. Both properties are of type Record<string, ExecutorsJsonEntry>, representing a mapping of string keys to ExecutorsJsonEntry objects.
