TITLE: Generating new React library with Nx
DESCRIPTION: Command to generate a new React library named 'mylib' using the Nx React plugin.
SOURCE: https://github.com/nrwl/nx/blob/master/nx-dev/tutorial/src/content/tutorial/2-react-monorepo/2r-smart-monorepo/2-use-preset/_solution/react-monorepo/README.md#2025-04-22_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: sh
CODE:
```
npx nx g @nx/react:lib mylib
```
